"title": "8359: weakness, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8359: weakness, spiritual",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Human standards of strength and weakness are overturned by God's perspective and may be used for his glory.</p>\n<h2>Spiritual weakness leads to increased reliance on God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:38\">MRK 14:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:19\">ROM 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:27-1Cor1:29\">1CO 1:27–1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:2-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:2–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>Weakness demonstrates the power of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:27\">1CO 1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:29-Isa40:31\">ISA 40:29–40:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4\">ISA 50:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:25\">JER 31:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:5-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:5–12:10</a></p>\n<h2>God helps those who are weak</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26\">ROM 8:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:29\">ISA 40:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:16\">EZK 34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:10\">JOL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:34\">HEB 11:34</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual weakness should not be despised</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1\">ROM 15:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:38\">MRK 14:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:1\">ROM 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:10\">1CO 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:7-1Cor8:12\">1CO 8:7–8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:22\">1CO 9:22</a></p>\n<h2>Overcoming spiritual weakness</h2>\n<h3>The importance of overcoming weakness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:12\">HEB 12:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:6-Josh1:7\">JOS 1:6–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:10\">JOL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:28-Matt6:33\">MAT 6:28–6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:11\">HEB 11:11</a></p>\n<h3>Weakness can be overcome by trusting in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:20\">ROM 4:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:30-Matt14:31\">MAT 14:30–14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:6-2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:6–1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:6\">JAS 1:6</a></p>",
